### Enter the issue address

Closes #230500

### Add your comment and screenshots

To reproduce:

1. UK VPN (mandatory — CMP only fires for UK/EU)
2. AdGuard Browser Extension MV3 with only Base + Tracking Protection + Social Media filters (reporter's exact config)
3. Clear cookies for birminghammail.co.uk
4. Visit any article — the consent popup should appear and be stuck

`#pp-prompt` paywall with no dismiss option; this appears after "Reject and Pay" button click - creates an unescapable loop.

By the way, blocking the `||premium.express.co.uk/js/dist/privacy-plus-v2.min.js^` root script hides the "Reject and Pay" and "I Accept" buttons, leaving users unable to interact at all :(

